==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sorbic
<hw>Sor"bic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>sorbique</ets>. See <er>Sorb</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Pertaining to, or obtained from, the rowan tree, or sorb;
specifically, designating an acid, C<?/H<?/CO<?/H, of the acetylene
series, found in the unripe berries of this tree, and extracted as a
white crystalline substance.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sorbile</ent>⟦br⟧
